FBIS4-58531 "drnes087_n_94009" FBIS-NES-94-087 Daily Report 4 May 1994 LEBANON Newspapers To Observe Work Stoppage 7 May Newspapers To Observe Work Stoppage 7 May NC0405173294 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 4 May 94 NC0405173294 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] In agreement with the Editors Union, the Lebanese Press Syndicate has issued a statement on a work stoppage by newspapers on Friday. Newspapers will not be published on 7 May. Head of the Lebanese intellectuals' academy Mayy al-Murr called on the state to proclaim the anniversary of the 6 May martyrs an anniversary for all Lebanese martyrs.
